":21.12,"text":"St. John's on the corner, steam on the glass Fingers in the ladle, tryin' not to ask"},{"s":21.12,"e":22.18,"text":"Who got next?"},{"s":22.26,"e":23.18,"text":"Who got less?"},{"s":23.92,"e":26.72,"text":"Same old shame, same old dress"},{"s":26.72,"e":35.28,"text":"I seen kings in line, I seen queens in line Pride in the back, hunger by design"},{"s":35.28,"e":42.2,"text":"And we all come in with a cracked up grin Little bit of sin, little bit of skin"},{"s":42.2,"e":49.5,"text":"Little bit of hope in a paper cup Say a small amen when the bowl fills up"},{"s":49.5,"e":55.94,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, let me survive"},{"s":55.94,"e":63.32,"text":"Under God's sky, we take what we can Bless this mouth, bless this man"},{"s":63.32,"e":69.86,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, I'm still inside"},{"s":69.86,"e":76.78,"text":"If love is real, let it come down here Come down here, come down here"},{"s":76.82,"e":81.38,"text":"I seen midnight kids with a dance floor stare Coke in the veins and a prayer in the air"},{"s":81.38,"e":84.88,"text":"Hearts like paper, boots worn thin Laughin' too loud at the shape that ends"},{"s":84.88,"e":88.16,"text":"Some want touch, some want grace Some wanna forget their own damn face"},{"s":88.16,"e":91.62,"text":"But the room stay warm when the tray rolls through Everybody needs somethin' true"},{"s":91.62,"e":98.32,"text":"And we all come in with a cracked up grin Little bit of sin, little bit of skin"},{"s":98.32,"e":106.48,"text":"Little bit of hope in a paper cup Say a small amen when the bowl fills up"},{"s":106.48,"e":112.92,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, let me survive"},{"s":112.92,"e":120.2,"text":"Under God's sky, we take what we can Bless this mouth, bless this man"},{"s":120.2,"e":126.72,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, I'm still inside"},{"s":126.72,"e":133.64,"text":"If love is real, let it come down here Come down here, come down here"},{"s":134.52,"e":137.76,"text":"When the world gets loud and the rent comes due"},{"s":137.76,"e":144.68,"text":"When the body froze and the night eats through I'll stand in line with my hands out too"},{"s":144.68,"e":150.32,"text":"Not above nobody, just passin' through"},{"s":150.78,"e":157.76,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, let me survive"},{"s":157.76,"e":164.58,"text":"Under God's sky, we take what we can Bless this mouth, bless this man"},{"s":164.58,"e":171.28,"text":"St. John's plate, keep me alive St. John's plate, I'm still inside"},{"s":171.28,"e":178.26,"text":"If love is real, let it come down here Come down here, come down here"},{"s":181.56,"e":183.12,"text":"Come down here"}],"duration":187.83999633789062,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:25:11.943Z","model":"whisper-1"}